{"id":303383,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-北京维权人士送西瓜声援外交部前维权者/","date":"2013-07-12T20:33:16Z","modified":"2013-07-12T20:33:16Z","title":"维权网 | 北京维权人士送西瓜声援外交部前维权者（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员回菁理报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，北京维权人士杨秋雨、倪玉兰的丈夫董继勤前往国家外交部门前，探望要求参加国家人权计划拟定、修改的维权公民，给他们送去了解暑的西瓜，并听在场冤民陈述冤情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据维权人士跟本网信息员反映，下午北京维权人士杨秋雨、倪玉兰的丈夫董继勤，给要求参与中国人权计划撰写而在外交部前日夜苦等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>天的大妈大姐送去西瓜。董继勤问一位外地大姐：为什么来外交部？大姐说：“我来外交部要人权等答复。”说着说着，那大姐不由的诉说起自己多年的冤情。董继勤说：虽说我没有完全听懂，但看大姐那一把鼻涕一把泪哭的非常伤心的样子，真让人心酸。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>开始，曹顺利、刘晓芳等人前往外交部，希望参与撰写起草国家人权报告，把上访群体的人权状况调查表交给他们，以作为编撰国家人权报告的主要信息来源。为了等待答复，大家日夜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时坚守在外交部门前。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>遭到清场，所有静坐人员被强制带离现场。随后，大家再次集聚在外交部等待答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>期间，北京维权人士胡佳、胡石根，自由作家杜斌，山东维权人士陈光福等人先后到现场支持慰问。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FV_V-xSqTGk/UeAiwzAZV6I/AAAAAAAAlLo/sUs7AyiEb0E/s1600/MOV1A5%5B12201307183550GMT%5D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"250\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FV_V-xSqTGk/UeAiwzAZV6I/AAAAAAAAlLo/sUs7AyiEb0E/s320/MOV1A5%5B12201307183550GMT%5D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dWvfhJV57os/UeAiwddtpEI/AAAAAAAAlLk/-l8eMkR3bWc/s1600/PIC_8002.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dWvfhJV57os/UeAiwddtpEI/AAAAAAAAlLk/-l8eMkR3bWc/s320/PIC_8002.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-U_SkbHIr_dY/UeAitI3zGSI/AAAAAAAAlLc/ZgQQMG3kIFk/s1600/PIC_7998.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-U_SkbHIr_dY/UeAitI3zGSI/AAAAAAAAlLc/ZgQQMG3kIFk/s320/PIC_7998.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}